<br>
If you want to get technical, there are starving people all over the world, while you sit here and complain about a video game. There are people dying all over the world. Why are you complaining? Atleast you have food. Atleast you're not getting shot at. You don't know how easy you have it.<br>
<br>
Sound familiar?<br>
<br>
So please don't turn this into &quot;Well I'm a Mage and my Epic sucks. You have no room to complain because your Epic isn't as hard as mine.&quot; argument. It's not my fault your Epic sucks. I didn't write the quest for it. <br>
<br>
And even still, would you argue that your Epic pet isn't 20x's better than the effect off of my epic? (55hp/tick DoT. 3min duration.) Risk &gt; Reward. My Epic is less risk, ergo it's a &quot;lesser&quot; reward.<br>
<br>
My complaint is triggerable mobs dropping dragon loot. My &quot;Epic&quot; fight only drops the Pod of Seawater. The effect is disgustingly low DPS. It's harder for me to convince people to run out to BFE in Timmy Deep to kill something no one but me benefits from. Where a Cleric, not only has their Epic effect people will always, always want as motivation to get people out there, but now their triggerable mob also drops loot for everyone else! <br>
<br>
It should be one way or the other. If triggerable mobs drop the loot of their &quot;real&quot; spawns, so be it. But either *all* triggerable mobs should or *none* of the triggerable mobs should. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/ueqfoulwind.showPublicProfile?language=EN>EQFoulwind</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_greenspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Cons Dubious </span><br>  Posts: 142<br> <font color=#333333>(9/25/02 7:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=200.topic&index=59>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://millennium.fortunecity.com/celesteville/649/oscar.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: best solution</span><hr size=1> Who's driving the WAAAAHHH-bulance ?<br>
